sourcesContent:
<template lang="pug">
    v-container#setting
        v-layout(wrap column)
            v-flex(xs12)
                .title.text-xs-left.mb-4 Setting
        v-layout(wrap)  
            v-flex(xs12 sm4 md4)
                v-select(v-model="select" :hint="`${select.domain_name}`" :items="items" item-text="domain_name" label="Select Domain" persistent-hint return-object single-line color="brown lighten-2") 
            v-flex(xs12 sm8 md8)
                v-tabs(fixed-tabs slider-color="brown lighten-2")
                    v-tab(v-for="tab in tabs" :href="tab.route") {{tab.title}}
        v-layout(wrap)
            v-flex(xs12)
                

</template>

<script>
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            select: { domain_name: "www.hiero7.com" },
            items: [
                {
                    domain_name: "www.hiero7.com",
                    cname: "www.mydomain1.com.shiftcdn.com"
                },
                {
                    domain_name: "www.yahoo.com",
                    cname: "www.yahoo.com.shiftcdn.com"
                },
                {
                    domain_name: "www.google.com",
                    cname: "www.google.com.shiftcdn.com"
                }
            ],
            tabs: [
                { title: "General", route: "admin/setting" },
                { title: "CDNs", route: "admin/settingCDN" },
                { title: "iRouteCDN", route: "admin/settingiRouteCDN" }
            ]
        };
    }
};
</script>
